&lt;h2 class=&quot;text-title text-title-width-large&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;GLG is The World’s Insight Network.&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;text-content text-content-width-large&quot; style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;In the past, professionals relied on friends, contacts, or mentors for business insights. GLG has changed that. Our clients can access vast on-demand expertise as they need it. Need expertise? We bring it right to you.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;GLG connects thousands of the world’s best businesses –– from Fortune 500 corporations to leading tech, professional services, and financial institutions –– to the largest and most varied source of first-hand expertise.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With offices in 13 countries, our global teams connect clients to powerful insights from our network of industry experts every day.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;We are always looking for smart, curious people to help us bring the power of insight to every great professional decision.&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Join our Client Solutions Team today!&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Our Client Solutions Associates are front-line client service professionals and the engine of GLG. They work closely with our clients in the leading industries on the critical decisions they make every day. These custom learning solutions include phone consultations and one-on-one meetings, as well as surveys, reports, and site tours with leading experts and C-suite executives.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Client Solutions Associates work in teams across industries, connecting our clients to the insight they need from leading doctors, academics, scientists, policy specialists, strategists, executives and other experts with years of on-the-ground experience. Client Solutions Associates themselves also develop into subject matter experts across industries and topics via their client service role.&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;In this role, you will undergo comprehensive training of which some of the key initial responsibilities include:&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Expanding GLG Councils and learning to effectively and clearly explain GLG’s value proposition and business model to leading industry thought leaders;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Engaging Council Members on a daily basis to understand their capabilities and knowledge on specific client requests;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Supporting senior team members on all aspects of client engagements; and&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Learning our compliance policies and procedures to protect the integrity of client engagements.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;As you progress in&amp;nbsp;this role you will gain more autonomy by:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Executing custom projects across client firms – including consultations, surveys, and special projects;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Continuing to expand GLG Councils;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Engaging with clients daily to understand their needs and provide exceptional service;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Maintaining accountability and responsibility for client projects and overall client experience;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Collaborating with our Business Development team on re

&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Job Title: Associate, Business Development&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Location: Mumbai, India&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Business Development, Corporate Markets (Industry Agnostic)&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The role of the Business Development Associate is to accelerate sales to expand the firm’s user base and offerings within companies across corporate markets in India &amp;amp; South Asia. The candidate will focus on identifying, qualifying, and closing new revenue opportunities as well as work on contract renewals, optimizing client experience, gaining market share, and pursuing excellence in close collaboration with a team of GLG servicing team professionals. This candidate will also have an opportunity to work with senior leaders across both the internal organization and within their clients, including developing partnerships with SVPs, EVPs and CXOs of large operating companies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Specific responsibilities include (but are not limited to):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Leverage professional network to build new relationships at operating companies and engage at a granular level with industry executives on topics of critical importance to their businesses.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with senior BD team members in securing enterprise-level agreements for both existing clients and new business opportunities.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify and engage with senior industry leaders within the Corporate segment to develop new relationships and grow existing business relationships&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Identify growth opportunities, build &amp;amp; execute acquisition targets, plans, and realize objectives by helping GLG become a preferred go to partner for clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Set roadmap for overall book of business and at the account level.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ensure overall client user satisfaction with GLG services and collaborate with servicing team to implement adjustments in servicing model when necessary&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop sales collateral and support the wider Corporate markets - Sales team with the production of promotional materials, especially around GLG’s new product offerings.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work creatively and collaboratively with internal colleagues- marketing, compliance, legal, finance, technology to deliver solutions to solve complex overall client business issues.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with GLG project teams to support execution and delivery of research projects, providing guidance and support as needed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with GLG&#39;s research teams to target new areas of opportunity and further develop the GLG&#39;s service product offering&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Key performance metrics&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
