&lt;li&gt;0-3 years of work experience preferably working in customer service / sales / head hunting / recruitment / market research&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;A keen interest in learning about various industries and communicating with senior executives on a daily basis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Bachelor&#39;s degree or higher from a top tier university&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;strong&gt;This is a Full-time role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
